data.description: VA assumable loan 2.625%!! 1% interest rate buy down with PLACE Mortgage. Welcome to this fabulous home located in the highly sought after petroglyphs!  This beautiful home is located in a culdesac and features mountain views!  The home offers great natural light and fabulous upgrades!  The upgrades include granite countertops, custom lighting throughout, beautiful travertine flooring and hardwood.  This home also features great natural light and a spacious loft upstairs in addition to the 4 bedrooms with a fabulous walk out deck that is enclosed!  Enjoy our beautiful weather with the private outdoor sitting area! This home is one of a kind and will not be available for long!  Call today for your own private showing!
